Package: archiver
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Michael Murwayi <michael@example.com>
Depends: python3, python3-psycopg2
Description: Archive files for all users in a Unix group
 A command-line tool that archives files for users in a given Unix group,
 preserving directory structure and logging archive operations to PostgreSQL
 when available.
